---

This repository is a derivative of nanoGPT (https://github.com/karpathy/nanoGPT)
by Andrej Karpathy, originally released under the MIT License.

Modifications and additions by Kourosh Salehi-Ashtiani include:
  - batch_inference.py: Batch inference script with six anti-repetition
    mitigations for protein sequence generation
  - train_.py: Modified training script for protein language models
  - config/train_par_gpt2-s_scratch.py: Training configuration for
    character-level protein language models
  - data/char_dark/, data/char_white/, data/char_algae/: Dataset preparation
    for dark, annotated, and combined algal proteome datasets
  - prompts_1000algae.csv: Example prompt file for protein sequence generation
